(Republished.)

Robert Koreska, Doing business as W. Koreska, Appellant, v. United Cargo Corp., Defendant-Respondent and Third-Party Plaintiff-Respondent. Parker Whitney Ltd., Third-Party Defendant-Respondent.

- — Order, entered on October 19, 1964, reversed on the law, with $30 costs and disbursements to appellant and the motion for summary judgment for $13,939.72, the invoice price, in favor of plaintiff, is granted. Concur — Breitel, Steuer and Bastow, JJ.; Botein, P. J., and Stevens, J., dissent in an opinion by Stevens, J. - The order of this court entered on April 1, 1965 [23 A D 2d 37] is vacated.
